lab1b-client.c: the C source file for the client. It provides the --port, --compress and the --log options.
--port requires users to provide the port#, it is mandatory.
--log is used to record the bytes sent and received.
--compress option to compress and decompress the bytes sent and received.

lab1b-server.c: the C source file for the server. It provide the --port and  --compress. It supports --shell option from the previous example.

Makefile: Compiles the programs and tar the following files:lab1b-client.c lab1b-server.c README Makefile


